      <title>调查发现银行在消息应用程序审查方面落后</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banks-falling-behind-messaging-app-scrutiny-survey-finds-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三发布的一项调查显示，全球金融公司在使用个人消息应用程序监控和存档所有业务相关通信方面落后，可能面临监管违规和罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banks-falling-behind-messaging-app-scrutiny-survey-finds-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
